All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
GameListener
This class extends KeyListener and listens for input from the player.
GameMenuBar
This class extends JMenuBar and represents the Menu for user to pick options.
GamePanel
This class extends JPanel and represents the main panel of the soccer game.
GamePlayer
This class implements Comparable and represents players of the game.
Goalkeeper
This class extends GamePlayer and represents the goalkeeper of the game.
MenubarListener
This class extends ActionListener and listens for menu selection by player.
MiniSoccerApp
Class to run soccer program.
PlayerCollection
This class extends Iterable and represents a collection of players as an ArrayList which includes Striker and Goalkeeper.
PlayerCollectionIterator
This class implements Iterator and represents the iterator for the PlayerCollection.
PlayerFactory
This is a factory class that creates players for the soccer game as per factory pattern.
PlayerStatistics
This class represents player statistics either count of catches or goals scored.
SoccerBall
This class uses Singleton pattern and represents a soccer ball.
SoccerGame
This class represents the soccer game and includes main features.
Striker
This class represents the Striker which is a type of GamePlayer.
